summary:
- **Results of General Meeting**: All resolutions passed with majority approval.  
- **Key Resolutions**:  
  - **Placement Share Ratification**: Ratification of prior placement shares under Listing Rules 7.1 and 7.1A (97.44% and 99.95% approval, respectively).  
  - **Director Re-elections**: Bevan Tarratt and Julian Woodcock re-elected (92.46% and 92.46% approval).  
  - **Employee Incentive Plan**: Re-approved (96% approval).  
  - **Director Performance Rights**: Issuance approved for Nathan Lude (90.25%), Steven Woodham (91.70%), Julian Woodcock (92.15%), and Bevan Tarratt (87.31%).  

No material capital markets or trading-sensitive actions identified beyond routine approvals.
